&lt;h2 id=&#34;重点-1满-16-周岁--备案完成&#34;&gt;重点 1：满 16 周岁 + 备案完成
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;首先重头戏的那肯定就是&lt;strong&gt;满 16 周岁&lt;/strong&gt;，所以在寒假期间我给我的域名整了&lt;strong&gt;icp 备案&lt;/strong&gt;以及&lt;strong&gt;公安备案&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;stack-lazy-picture&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/8c3230204067/9ec4f041b85f/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/8c3230204067/9ec4f041b85f/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/8c3230204067/9ec4f041b85f/responsive_content-1440.avif 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/8c3230204067/9ec4f041b85f/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/8c3230204067/9ec4f041b85f/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/8c3230204067/9ec4f041b85f/responsive_content-1440.webp 1440w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img
