        <item>
        <title>博客的起因经过结果</title>
        <link>https://whylove.top/p/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%B7%E5%9B%A0%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C/</link>
        <pubDate>Sun, 18 Jan 2026 19:51:46 +0800</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://whylove.top/p/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%B7%E5%9B%A0%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://whylove.top/p/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%B7%E5%9B%A0%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C/aliyun-server.jpg" alt="Featured image of post 博客的起因经过结果" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;纯粹是闲出屁来了，最开始是因为在b站上看到有推销服务器的，恰巧我当时对这个比较感兴趣。&lt;strong&gt;于是我就在想我是不是也可以整一台云服务器&lt;/strong&gt;，当机立断就找妈妈要了100块钱，然后就在网上选到了阿里云的&lt;strong&gt;2h2g加峰值200m宽带&lt;/strong&gt;，&lt;span class=&#34;stack-lazy-picture&#34; data-lazy-state=&#34;preview&#34;&gt;&lt;picture&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/avif&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/116e1d7c8369/responsive_content-320.avif 320w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/116e1d7c8369/responsive_content-480.avif 480w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/116e1d7c8369/responsive_content-1264.avif 1264w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;source type=&#34;image/webp&#34; data-srcset=&#34;https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/116e1d7c8369/responsive_content-320.webp 320w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/116e1d7c8369/responsive_content-480.webp 480w, https://whylove.top/generated/image-variants/9b21c52949b4/116e1d7c8369/responsive_content-1264.webp 1264w&#34; sizes=&#34;(min-width: 1024px) 864px, (min-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 64px), calc(100vw - 32px)&#34;&gt;&lt;img
    src=&#34;https://whylove.top/p/%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%B7%E5%9B%A0%E7%BB%8F%E8%BF%87%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C/aliyun-server_hu_3a8f5c1ba73dca12.jpg&#34;
